  SCIENCE FACTS
============================================================

Domain:  Biology
Topic:   ATP
Formula: ADP + Pi → ATP
Note:    Universal energy currency of all living cells

Domain:  Biology
Topic:   Cell Theory
Formula: All life is made of cells arising from pre-existing cells
Note:    Foundation of modern biology

Domain:  Medicine
Topic:   Blood Types
Formula: ABO system + Rh factor
Note:    Determines blood transfusion compatibility

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Wave Equation
Formula: v = fλ
Note:    Speed of wave = frequency × wavelength

Domain:  Biology
Topic:   Central Dogma
Formula: DNA → RNA → Protein
Note:    Information flow in all living organisms

